{"tid":771814,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《工作細胞》舞台劇血小板演員公開  真小蘿莉萌翻天","createTime":"2018-08-08T09:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T03:05:31.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4e34acc0aa0e77b30d41246bd4ce1e20533f2cd4","tid":771814,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"之前《工作細胞》宣布推出舞台劇並且公開了紅血球和白血球的定妝照，效果還是非常還原。不過大家都在期待血小板的定妝照，今天官方終於公開了血小板的演員，竟然真的是小蘿莉，而且還是3個，感覺粉絲們要瘋狂了。除此之外作品中其它常見的細胞都公開演員表，T細胞、巨噬細胞、樹狀細胞、初始T細胞等都會登場，感覺這個舞台劇一定會非常有趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171814_8f0835abf68c8e53beb6230fb3710208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171814_8f0835abf68c8e53beb6230fb3710208.jpg&h=09da7bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岸田結光、木內彩音、森田恵將出演血小板，三個小蘿莉真是非常可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171835_06bab362892e4e73fd56ba00874df00c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171835_06bab362892e4e73fd56ba00874df00c.jpg&h=6f5307d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171837_db42c9787e13bbabe3ff74b9f307d084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171837_db42c9787e13bbabe3ff74b9f307d084.jpg&h=15df579d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171839_29f22e0aa97cc08d5fd044f39a2bbbe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171839_29f22e0aa97cc08d5fd044f39a2bbbe9.jpg&h=9d91ecca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《工作細胞》是由清水茜創作的一部細胞擬人化的漫畫。作品中，人體內的細胞生態被描繪成如同人類社會一樣的環境，其中白血球負責與病毒戰鬥，紅血球負責輸送氧氣，血小板則負責止血等等。每個類型的細胞都有著自己相應的工作，它們在自己的崗位上兢兢業業，而當有病毒或者細菌入侵時，細胞們就會團結起來共同作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171859_4e17485fc147ea6653664b9b23eff21f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171859_4e17485fc147ea6653664b9b23eff21f.jpg&h=f8212e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT細胞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/171913_97e40fd75e872bf8731053f68a28defa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F171913_97e40fd75e872bf8731053f68a28defa.jpg&h=52a7cbb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巨噬細胞"},{"pid":"5f18cc3b7a1dc0598416e34fdc3c7b5efdac92a7","tid":771814,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"呀囉呢呀囉呢"},{"pid":"70a76ab1393d70ae83f9d2dd5e0d576d22dbcf51","tid":771814,"uid":148749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"三次元就二次元唯一相近既地方就係蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76557688982e1719428a038efbf4c71bf1a1af3","tid":771814,"uid":49275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"就咁睇圖都覺得佢地嘈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a7abf86a772b7432108aa9826c9013b24e0cc9","tid":771814,"uid":85762,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"第三個血小板同前面兩個差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0dee329c71574067e9a720fcecc7cd877611a0","tid":771814,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"FBI"},{"pid":"3d276eec1eaac9f8cbf7cdf9641f8537ef606fb0","tid":771814,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"巨噬細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src